## 4️⃣ Integration Plan

### 4.1 — Donation System

**File:** [donation.service.js](file:///Users/mohamedyaser/Documents/LifeLink/src/services/donation.service.js)

**Trigger points:**

| Location | Event | Activity Payload |
|----------|-------|-----------------|
| `createDonation()` — after `Donation.create()` succeeds (line ~63) | Donation created | `type: "donation"`, `action: "created_donation"`, `referenceId: donation._id`, `referenceType: "Donation"`, `metadata: { requestType, bloodType/organType, hospitalName }` |
| `updateDonationStatus()` — inside the `if (status === 'completed')` block (line ~119) | Donation completed | `type: "donation"`, `action: "completed_donation"`, `referenceId: donation._id`, `metadata: { quantity, completedDate }` |
| `cancelDonation()` — after status set to cancelled (line ~240) | Donation cancelled | `type: "donation"`, `action: "cancelled_donation"`, `referenceId: donation._id` |

**Integration pattern:** Fire-and-forget. Call `activityService.logActivity().catch(e => logger.error(...))` — exactly the same pattern used for reward triggers at line 125-133 of `donation.service.js`.

### 4.2 — Reward System

**File:** [reward.service.js](file:///Users/mohamedyaser/Documents/LifeLink/src/services/reward.service.js)

**Trigger points:**

| Location | Event | Activity Payload |
|----------|-------|-----------------|
| `awardPoints()` — after successful transaction commit (line ~118) | Points earned | `type: "reward"`, `action: "earned_points"`, `referenceId: transaction._id`, `referenceType: "PointsTransaction"`, `metadata: { pointsAmount, transactionType, description, balanceAfter }` |
| `redeemReward()` — after successful redemption (line ~468) | Reward redeemed | `type: "reward"`, `action: "redeemed_reward"`, `referenceId: redemption._id`, `referenceType: "RewardRedemption"`, `metadata: { rewardName, pointsSpent, confirmationCode }` |
| `checkAndUpdateBadges()` — inside the `if (!wasAlreadyUnlocked)` block (line ~264) | Badge unlocked | `type: "reward"`, `action: "badge_unlocked"`, `referenceId: badge._id`, `metadata: { badgeName, rarity }` |
| `awardPoints()` — inside `if (result?.tierChanged)` block (line ~131) | Tier promotion | `type: "reward"`, `action: "tier_promoted"`, `referenceId: donorId`, `metadata: { newTier, bonusPoints }` |

### 4.3 — Urgent Requests (Accept / Decline)

**File:** [donor.controller.js](file:///Users/mohamedyaser/Documents/LifeLink/src/controllers/donor.controller.js)

**Trigger points:**

| Location | Event | Activity Payload |
|----------|-------|-----------------|
| `respondToRequest()` — after `Donation.create()` succeeds (line ~157) | Accepted urgent/normal request | `type: "emergency_response"` (if urgency is high/critical, else `"donation"`), `action: "accepted_urgent_request"`, `referenceId: donation._id`, `metadata: { requestType, urgency, hospitalName }` |
| `declineUrgentRequest()` — after `Donation.create()` with cancelled status (line ~456) | Declined urgent request | `type: "emergency_response"`, `action: "declined_urgent_request"`, `referenceId: declinedResponse._id`, `metadata: { reason, urgency }` |

### 4.4 — Profile Updates

**File:** [donor.controller.js](file:///Users/mohamedyaser/Documents/LifeLink/src/controllers/donor.controller.js)

**Trigger points:**

| Location | Event | Activity Payload |
|----------|-------|-----------------|
| `updateProfile()` — after successful `findByIdAndUpdate` (line ~52) | Profile updated | `type: "profile_update"`, `action: "updated_profile"`, `referenceId: null` (no dedup — each update is a valid activity), `metadata: { fieldsUpdated: ["fullName", "bloodType", ...] }` |
| `updateHealthHistory()` — after successful save (line ~341) | Health history updated | `type: "profile_update"`, `action: "updated_health_history"`, `referenceId: null`, `metadata: { fieldsUpdated: [...] }` |

